00:24:13,972 --> 00:24:16,057
<b>But when they applied
Einstein's theory of relativity</b>

389
00:24:16,141 --> 00:24:18,268
<b>to the tracking process--</b>

390
00:24:18,351 --> 00:24:19,769
<b>That ID already exists.</b>

391
00:24:20,687 --> 00:24:22,939
