when I am the King?</b>

392
00:24:24,315 --> 00:24:25,442
<b>Go for "King Two."</b>

393
00:24:26,234 --> 00:24:28,236
<b>Anyway, about the theory of relativity--</b>

394
00:24:28,319 --> 00:24:30,113
<b>All Kings are taken until King 987.</b>

395
00:24:31,990 --> 00:24:33,825
<b>Track the IP addresses
of those 988 people.</b>

396
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,369
<b>Right now.</b>

397
