402
00:24:53,094 --> 00:24:56,765
<b>We're already facing trouble
with our Japanese competitors</b>

403
00:24:56,848 --> 00:24:59,350
<b>regarding the patent of our PRS system--</b>

404
00:24:59,434 --> 00:25:02,228
<b>Did you prepare a presentation
to tell me that we can't do it?</b>

405
00:25:02,771 --> 00:25:06,441
