<i><b>That woman keeps saying
we need to spend more on national defense</i></b>

421
00:25:53,029 --> 00:25:55,198
<i><b>when she doesn't even know anything.</i></b>

422
00:25:55,281 --> 00:25:56,866
<i><b>That will only upset the Japanese.</i></b>

423
00:25:57,992 --> 00:26:01,412
<b>Congressman Park was
at Jeguk University's homecoming event.</b>

424
00:26:01,496 --> 00:26:04,415
<b>A few reporters from that university
were apparently there, too.</b>

425
00:26:06,668 --> 00:26:08,253
<i><b>I'm sick of hearing her say that.</i></b>

426
00:26:08,753 --> 00:26:12,674
<i><b>Japan is our ally.
Are you trying to start a war with them?</i></b>

427
00:26:13,341 --> 00:26:17,679
<i><b>I bet she only cares about
what she's going to wear every day.</i></b>

428
00:26:17,971 --> 00:26:20,849
