432
00:26:29,232 --> 00:26:30,400
<i><b>And I already asked him.</i></b>

433
00:26:30,483 --> 00:26:32,235
<b>Should I kill this jerk?</b>

434
00:26:32,986 --> 00:26:34,195
<b>What?</b>

435
00:26:34,487 --> 00:26:36,447
<b>Look at me. Does my nose look fake?</b>

436
00:26:36,531 --> 00:26:38,658
<b>It's probably because it looks so perfect.</b>

437
00:26:39,284 --> 00:26:40,118
<b>Right?</b>

438
00:26:41,744 --> 00:26:44,289
<b>Then let's just make him
regret that he's alive.</b>

439
00:26:52,255 --> 00:26:54,465
<b>Send this to Reporter Song.
